    "# screen 基础\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "### 使用问题\n",
    "\n",
    "1. Cannot open your terminal '/dev/pts/0' - please check.\n",
    "\n",
    "```bash\n",
    "解决方法:\n",
    "# 运行脚本\n",
    "script -q -c \"su $USER -l -c 'screen -m -d -S $NAME $DAEMON start'\" /dev/null\n",
    "\n",
    "# 单独执行\n",
    "script /dev/null\n",
    "\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n"
   ]
  }
